    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials"| S3
    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key"| LLMProviders

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/5000<br/>GET /metrics<br/>No auth"| Metrics

